# BROWSER-replies.md - Notifications Page Reply Patterns

**Notifications URL:** `https://bsky.app/notifications`
**Page test ID:** `data-testid="notifsFeed"` — container for notification items.

## S 1. Extract Unreplied Posts (Notifications Page)

Navigate to `https://bsky.app/notifications`, then extract with 3s embedded wait.
Empty result is normal — new or quiet accounts will have zero notifications. Accept it and move to § 4.

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000)); var containers = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('div[role=\"link\"]')); var results = []; var seen = {}; for (var i = 0; i < containers.length; i++) { if (results.length >= 10) break; var container = containers[i]; var link = container.querySelector('a[href*=\"/post/\"]'); if (!link) continue; var parts = link.href.split('/post/'); if (parts.length < 2) continue; var postId = parts[1].split('/')[0].split('?')[0]; if (seen[postId]) continue; seen[postId] = true; var text = container.innerText; if (text.includes('{{handle}}')) continue; var lines = text.split(String.fromCharCode(10)).filter(function(l) { return l.trim(); }); results.push({ url: link.href, postId: postId, author: lines[0] || 'unknown', preview: lines.slice(1).join(' ').slice(0, 200) }); } return results; }"}
ENDJSON
```

---

## S 2. Open Reply Dialog on Notification Post

**Requires `allowedIds`** — array of post IDs from grep pre-check (step 3b).

Navigate to the post URL, then use S 4b (Compose reply click) + S 5 (type and submit).

On Bluesky notifications page, clicking a notification navigates to the post page directly. From there, use the standard compose reply flow:

1. Navigate to post URL
2. Run BROWSER-engage.md S 4b (click "Compose reply")
3. Run BROWSER-core.md S 5 (type + submit)

This is different from Threads where replies happen via popup from activity page. On Bluesky, always navigate to the post page first.
